description.content:
The hotel is located just 4 km away from the Chikalthana airport, 7 km from the railway station and 7 km from the bus station and city centre. The nearest international airports are Mumbai and Pune respectively. The city offers excellent rail links to a number of destinations.

This air-conditioned city hotel is reputed for its superb standard of service and the huge variety of cuisines available in its restaurant. It can host gatherings of up to 6000 people in its various banquet halls and on its vast manicured lawns. The guest facilities include an entrance hall with 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility, lift access, a café, a bar, a business centre, a shopping arcade and a travel desk. There is also an on-site barber and ladies' beauty parlour and, for an additional fee, guests may make use of the room and laundry services. Parking is available for those arriving by car.

The rooms are recently renovated and are elegantly furnished. Each is equipped with an en suite bathroom, a minibar, seating, a desk, a safe, a TV, Internet access and a direct dial telephone. The air conditioning is centrally regulated.

The hotel offers the largest health club in the region, with facilities for squash for a fee, as well as a billiard table (charges apply), a sauna, a steam room (separate for male and female guests), massage (charges apply) and a fully equipped gym. There is also a swimming pool with sunken bar (charges apply), tennis and badminton courts (charges apply), a jogging track, card and carom rooms and more.

The Garbah, an ethnic-style bar, is the only one of its kind in Aurangabad, and serves the finest selection of Indian and foreign spirits, as well as a range of bar snacks. Society, a renovated, multi-cuisine restaurant, serves Indian, Chinese and Continental food. The grandeur of a bygone era is recreated in this restaurant, which oozes splendour and elegance.

The hotel is located off of the Nashik-Bombay highway, just minutes from the centre of Aurangabad. Nearby points of interest include the Panchakki watermill, the Aurangabad caves, Daulatabad Fort and Bibi Ka Maqbara mausoleum, often referred to as India's mini Taj Mahal. The hotel is 12 km from the Chikkalthana airport, 4 km from the railway station and 13 km from the bus station.

This hotel is a classic country resort, featuring clusters of cottages, enveloped in green verdant surroundings. In the lobby, natural light filters through the high circular dome skylight, creating a soothing ambience amidst the earth-tone furnishings. The air-conditioned hotel comprises a total of 48 guest rooms. Facilities on offer include 24-hour check in, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility, a bar, a restaurant, conference facilities and, for an additional fee, room and laundry services. Parking is provided for those arriving by car.

The spacious rooms are tastefully decorated with marble bathrooms and feature individual patios overlooking the pool or the gardens. All rooms offer TV, Internet access, tea and coffee making facilities, a hairdryer, an in-room desk, a safe and turn down and wake-up services. Some rooms come equipped with refrigerators. The heating and air conditioning is individually adjustable, and non-smoking rooms are available.

The hotel offers a billiard room, a health spa (charges apply), an indoor Jacuzzi hot tub, lit outdoor tennis courts, a massage therapist (charges apply), an outdoor pool with children's paddling section, table tennis, a playground, a pool table, a sauna and a steam room (charges apply). Guests can also enjoy a game of volleyball or badminton.

The Four Seasons Restaurant and Lounge is adjacent to the outdoor pool, serving international specialties and delicacies from India's vibrant culinary culture.

Be it for business or leisure, a wide range of services and amenities coupled with our intuitive understanding of your needs ensures that every detail is well attended to. 

For your convenience, our fully-equipped Business Centre offers a host of business services and facilities, while our insightful concierge service is eager to put together a personalised itinerary for you based on your interests.

24 hour in-room dining, a wireless Internet connection, babysitting services and a doctor on call are just some of our services that will ensure that your every need is taken care of. If you are looking to relax or unwind, The scenic resort also offers exciting recreational services, such a a 24-hour fitness centre and Camp Hyatt for younger guests.

This city hotel is a short drive from many historical sights and shopping opportunities. A variety of restaurants and cocktail lounges are located in the surrounding area - a business, commercial and entertainment centre. Hyderabad Railway Station is just opposite the hotel and is therefore within walking distance. Secunderabad Railway Station is about 5 km from the hotel. The hotel is located 20 km and around 45 minutes away from the new Hyderabad International Airport.

This air-conditioned hotel was renovated in 2008 and contains a total of 95 guest rooms over 4 storeys. There is a 24-hour reception, hotel safe, currency exchange facilities, a cloakroom and lift access. The hotel also has a pub, restaurant, conference facilities and a car park. For an additional fee, guests can use the Internet access and room and laundry services.

The hotel features well appointed, luxurious, air-conditioned rooms and suites designed to enhance the comfort of the business traveller. The hotel has a few carpeted and otherwise granite-floored rooms with 24-hour room service, hot/cold running water, minibar, Internet access, multi-channel TV and climate control. Other facilities include a direct dial telephone, safe and tea and coffee making facilities. Business class and non-smoking rooms are also available on request.

There is a snooker table at the hotel pub (fees apply).

The Venue is the hotel's multi-cuisine restaurant. Café Capri is the hotel coffee shop and is also a multi-cuisine restaurant. The hotel has an in-house pub called One Flight Down which offers a range of wines, beers and spirits with premium brands.

This hotel is located in the centre of Hyderabad's business, commercial and entertainment areas. Guests will also find a variety of restaurants and cocktail lounges located in the surrounding area of the hotel. The railway station is about 1 km from the hotel and the local bus station is about 4 km away (15-20 minutes). It is situated close to Lumbini Park, Osmania University, NTR Garden, HITEX exhibition centre and the Salarjung Museum, the 3rd largest museum in India and home to the biggest single collection of antiques. Hyderabad International Airport is 30 km from the hotel, a journey of about 90 minutes from the hotel.

This is a fine business-class city hotel and comprises a total of 53 rooms spread over 4 floors. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility and lift access. There is also a restaurant and business travellers will appreciate the business centre with access to copy and fax services as well as high-speed Internet access. The hotel also offers a meeting room for conferences. Guests can take advantage of the room and laundry services (both for an additional fee) and there is parking available for those arriving by car.

All the hotel's rooms are designed to provide a relaxing and comfortable atmosphere, with modern wood furniture. They feature specially designed headboards with light features, stylish chrome fittings and bright colours. All rooms come with a private bathroom with a shower. They are equipped with direct dial telephone, cable TV, Internet access, a safe, a fridge and a coffee maker. Some rooms have a desk and a safe, and individually-regulated air conditioning units are provided in all accommodation as standard.

The hotel offers a rooftop restaurant serving breakfast, lunch and dinner.

This resort is set among swaying palms in the quiet village of Betalbatim in south Goa. It lies away from all the hustle and bustle and yet has a convenient location, just 6 km from Margao railway terminus. Guests will find a selection of local handicrafts, textiles and other shops, as well as a few bars and restaurants, just 2 km from the resort. The accommodation is some 12 km from Dabolim Airport.

This villa-style hotel comprises 36 deluxe double rooms and 2 cottages. Its quiet location makes it an ideal place to relax and soak up the sun on the endless stretches of golden sands at Betalbatim Beach, which is only a short walk away. All in all, it is an ideal place for an unforgettable holiday. Facilities include a lobby with a 24-hour reception service and currency exchange. There is a bar and restaurant on site and room and laundry services are provided.

Each guest room at this resort has been tastefully designed. The accommodation comes well equipped with individually regulated air conditioning, a satellite TV and a minibar. Guests can relax in the bathtub in the three-fixture bathroom with hot and cold running water, or curl up with a favourite book on the veranda, which overlooks the landscaped lawns.

Guests can go swimming in the outdoor pool or lounge on the pool deck and soak up the sun, whilst cooling down with exotic cocktails or appetizers from the poolside bar. As evening falls, guests can watch the poolside come alive with the weekly barbecues and theme nights, and tap their feet to the live jazz, retro or reggae band.

Primavera is the elegant, air-conditioned all-day dining à la carte restaurant. It features an outdoor terrace that overlooks the pool.

This resort is centrally located in the busy resort area of Calangute and is great for exploring all the local area attractions, restaurants and bars. It lies 12 km from Panjim and 14 km from Tivim railway station. Goa Airport is 45 km away.

This club resort comprises a total of 89 bright rooms and provides a comfortable and friendly base for guests. Facilities on offer to guests include a lobby area with a 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility, a cloakroom and a bar. 

It also offers a restaurant, room and laundry services (both for an additional fee) and parking for those arriving by car.

The resort rooms are fabulously decorated with lots of natural light pouring in. They come with a private bathroom with a shower, as well as cable TV, a double bed, a telephone, a cupboard, a dressing table and a luggage rack. The rooms also feature either a balcony or a terrace.

The hotel features an outdoor swimming pool with a poolside snackbar (charges apply).

The resort offers a restaurant serving Indian, Chinese and local Goan fare.

"The hotel is conveniently situated on the colourful Candolim Road, Goa, India and is close to many local shops and restaurants. It is also just a mere 5 minute walk to the beautiful Candolim beach. This hotel offers 150 rooms and has a lobby area, a swimming pool, safe deposit facilities at an additional charge, and currency exchange facilities. Other services include taxis for hire, a 24-hour security service and a doctor on call. The hotel has a swimming pool with a children's section, a mini gym and a beauty salon. Safe deposit lockers are available at an additional cost and payable locally. The hotel has a restaurant named Obalcao, which serves international cuisine. This hotel offers a comfortable and convenient environment that welcomes all our guests and is the ideal setting for a pleasant stay at a reasonable price."

Hotel Lua Nova , Baga. This picturesque 25-room resort awaits to provide you a holiday at a perfectly tranquil and passionate Goan village environment.

Located a mere 40-minute drive from Goa's Dabolim Int'l. Airport, 12-km from Capital city Panjim and a bare 7-km from Goa's tourist-popular Mapusa market town. We are within convenient reach of Goa's trendy spots of tourist interest and all basic services - banks, exchange facilities, travel agencies, post office, markets & shopping arcades.

 A short stroll along beach-line takes you to Candolim – another popular North Goa tourist village, while a little hike across picturesque Baga hillock brings you to Goa's famed Anjuna Beach.

This charming and lovely holiday resort offers the ideal choice of accommodation for all those travellers who want to relax in a paradisiacal setting. 

The property is conveniently positioned in Goa, within easy reach from one of the most beautiful beaches in India, Calangute Baga.

This hotel is located in the heart of the city and is very close to the major business districts and the tourist attractions of Kolkata, such as the Kolkata High Court, which was founded in 1757 and was the original Supreme Court of India. Other nearby attractions include the Town Hall, Central Secretariat Building and the world-famous Eden Gardens, which is an international centre for the sport of cricket. The hotel is 15 minutes from the Howrah railway station and a 20-minute drive from the Netaji Subhash Chandra Bose International Airport, which is about 18 km away.

This is an urban resort, floating on the River Hooghly only 100 yards from the shore. The River Hooghly is a centre-point of Indian history and the hotel brings back that history in all its splendour, harking back to a time when Calcutta was in her finest glory. The 61-room floating hotel is based on the concept of combining the best qualities of a luxury cruise ship with the beauty of a world-class hotel permanently anchored in the city centre of Kolkata. The grounds consist of a promenade walkway by the river, a beautifully landscaped garden, centrally air-conditioned reception areas with a 24-hour reception desk, open-air banquet halls and a promenade deck. The hotel also provides a hotel safe, currency exchange facilities, a cloakroom, lift access, a hairdressing salon, a TV lounge, conference facilities, Internet access (fees apply) and a car park. For dining and drinks, guests can enjoy the on-site bar, restaurant and night club. Room and laundry services are on offer as well (fees apply for both).

This hotel is located 6 km from Hyderabad railway station (25 minutes' journey) and 8 km from Secundrabad railway station. It lies some 25 km from the new Hyderabad International Airport, a journey of about an hour.

This is a city business hotel which comprises a total of 46 well-appointed, spacious rooms and serviced apartments. It offers guests elegant hospitality, friendly staff, personalised service and excellent amenities, to make guests' stay at the hotel a comfortable one. The hotel is located in heart of the city at Banjara Hills, in close proximity to the corporate centre and the bustling business and shopping areas. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a 24-hour reception, a currency exchange facility, a cloakroom and lift access as well as a hairdressing salon. There is a pub and a multi-cuisine restaurant and business travellers will appreciate the conference facilities, board room, business centre and secretarial services. Guests can also take advantage of the concierge service, the Internet access (charges apply), 24-hour room service (charges apply) and the laundry/dry cleaning service (for an additional fee). Parking is available for those arriving by car.

All rooms come with a private bathroom with a shower and a hairdryer (on request). They are equipped with a direct dial telephone, satellite TV, Internet access, an electronic safe and a minibar. Furthermore, tea and coffee making facilities and air conditioning units are provided in all accommodation as standard.

Sports enthusiasts may enjoy a work-out in the well equipped gym (charges apply) and guests can relax in the sauna or steam room or with a massage treatment (all for an additional fee).

The hotel has a multi-cuisine restaurant named Tabla. A pub called Liquids and a leisure lounge are also available.

This hotel is located at a prime address in the heart of the central business district of the city. It lies some 12 km from Hyderabad railway station and it takes about 45 minutes to reach from the hotel depending on the traffic conditions. Secunderabad railway station is also approximately 12 km away and the new Hyderabad International Airport is 35 km from the hotel.

This city hotel is brisk, buzzing and purely business establishment. The hotel comprises a total of 16 rooms and features contemporary style, cutting-edge amenities and smart service combined to give the guests a personalised experience. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility, a cloakroom and lift access. There is a restaurant and guests can take advantage of the 24-hour room service. Laundry service is available for an additional fee and there is parking for those arriving by car.

All rooms come with a private bathroom with a bathtub, 24-hour hot and cold running water and a hairdryer. They are equipped with a direct dial telephone, satellite/ cable TV, WLAN Internet access, a minibar and an electronic safe. Furthermore, tea and coffee making facilities and individually regulated air conditioning are provided in all accommodation as standard.

Sports enthusiasts may enjoy a work-out in the gym.

The hotel offers a small sitting area where buffets are set up for breakfast only. Lunch and dinner are served in the rooms.

description.content:
The hotel is located in the Aravali hill range, near to the Jaipur exit from the Delhi motorway. It takes 25 minutes to reach the railway station and the local bus stop, and the hotel is located just 20 km, or 45 minutes, from the Jaipur Airport.

This city hotel, built in 2007, was designed in the style of ancient Rajasthani architecture, including the haveli appearance. The hotel offers a business centre with conference facilities, Internet browsing (for a fee), fax and photocopying facilities. An on-call doctor is available as well as parking facilities. The hotel comprises 24 rooms on 3 floors and offers 24-hour reception, hotel safe, currency exchange facilities, cloakroom and restaurant. There is room service and laundry service available for a fee.

The hotel's spacious and elegantly appointed rooms have exotic views of Amer Fort and the hills in the distance. Each room is tastefully designed to meet the basic comforts and needs of guests. The interiors are carefully chosen to provide a relaxing atmosphere with the perfect ambiance to relieve the stress of the weary tourist. All of the rooms have an attached bathroom with hot and cold running water and a shower. They additionally have a fridge, colour satellite/cable television, a direct dial telephone and individually regulated air conditioning as well as other modern amenities. Round-the-clock room service is available.

The Ethnic Restaurant offers continental, Chinese and Mughal cuisine, while the hotel's rooftop restaurant offers a choice of Indian and international dishes. It has a panoramic view of temples, the City Palace, old havelis and beautiful views of Jaipur and its surroundings.

This hotel is situated between Anjuna, which hosts a highly popular flea market on Wednesdays, and Mapusa, location of the Friday bazaar and Saturday market. Travelling from the Dabolim International Airport takes about an hour and the Konkan Railway Station at Tivim-Sirsaim is about 20 minutes away.

This family-run hotel is located amidst the peace, tranquillity and simplicity of the emerald valley of Assagao in North Goa. The heritage property nestles in the cool shade of mature mango trees and swaying coconut palms, in a naturally terraced landscape. It is a perfect place for guests to unwind in nature, to the song of exotic birds in the lush valley. The hotel features a lobby and restaurant, and room service is also available. For guests wishing to bring their vehicles, there is a car park on site.

The main section of this hotel is a 200-year-old Portuguese colonial mansion. The modern extension features a tiled roof, typical of the traditional Goan building style. The 20 well-appointed rooms are comfortable and come with a balcony and fridge as standard. Room service and prompt laundry services are also available to guests.

There are yoga lessons available in the hotel.

There is a pub and restaurant on site specialising in multiple cuisines, with a special emphasis on typical Goan food cooked in the traditional way, using spices from the hotel garden. Goan dishes on the menu include Chicken Cafreal, Goan Fish-Curry-Rice, Samarem, Fish Recheada, Sorpotel, Goan pork sausages, Ham, San'nas and Ale-bele. The kitchen will be happy to cater to guests' specific tastes and wishes.

"This resort is located in Goa, India is nestled among mango groves and between coconut palms. It is set slightly back from the road and just 100 metres from the beach. The resort is around 45 kms from Goa's Dabolim Airport.

Surrounded by gardens and sand dunes, this beach resort offers accommodation for short and long-stay guests throughout the year. It comprises a total of 34 rooms spread over 2 floors. The rooms are simply decorated but offer guests all they need. The resort features an outdoor swimming pool with a poolside bar. The hotel has its own private beach shack, The Calamari, which offers plenty of sun loungers for lazing around, as well as a restaurant serving a variety of cuisines to get guests' taste buds going. This resort will enchant the guests with its warm hospitality and surrounding beauty."

A true gem among the medium-category hotels in North Goa, Santana Beach Resort has, in a short time-span, become one of the most popular hotels in the area. Located on one of the many stunning sandy beaches in Goa, this family-run hotel is set in lush, tropical gardens - offering a charm found in few other hotels.

This little treasure stretches from the main Candolim-Sinquerim road, all the way down to the beach. It boasts 2 swimming pools, one of which has a sunken bar, a poolside restaurant. The rooms are cool and airy, and are contemporary in design. Delicious offerings from the kitchen make Olegario's Restaurant a must; enjoy fresh local ingredients as you dine 'al fresco' by the swimming pool.

It's the natural beauty, dazzling colors and of course fantastic goan hospitality that brings people back to Goa year after year, and when combined with the extra special comfort of a stay at Santana Beach Resort, a truly memorable vacation is guaranteed. When you've enjoyed a day at the beach or perhaps a morning at one of the colourful Goan markets, it's great to return to a cool room in one of the friendliest hotels in

The hotel is located 5 minutes from Calangute beach in North Goa, in the heart of the village. It is 45 km away from the airport.

This 65-room hotel offers simple and comfortable rooms in a friendly atmosphere. Facilities include a travel desk, currency exchange facilities and, for an additional cost, safety deposit lockers. Medical care is also available if required. There is a restaurant on site and parking is provided for guests.

The standard rooms are spacious and have double or twin beds, with an attached bathroom and shower & WC, ceiling fan, fridge, television, Intercom telephone, and balcony. Air- Condition Supplement available at an additional charge and payable locally and subject to availability.

There is a swimming pool, gym and beauty salon on site. Guests may also play table tennis.

The hotel restaurant offers a wide range of exotic dishes based on different international cuisines.

"This hotel is situated in Gurgaon, the ever-growing corporate hub in the National Capital Region of New Delhi, India. It is just off the NH8 expressway and close to Unitech Business Park and Signature Tower. Indira Gandhi International Airport is located approximately 16 kms from the hotel, and the domestic airport is approximately 18 kms away. The hotel has exquisitely furnished rooms with all the modern amenities and facilities. The hotel features an indoor swimming pool and health club with gym and spa. The Downtown Cafe is a multi-cuisine restaurant and offers a buffet for breakfast, lunch and dinner. An à la carte menu with a wide selection of Indian, continental and Chinese cuisine is also available. The 29th The Grill serves grilled dishes. The Bar Lounge offers a fine wine list and a wide selection of liquors. For convenience, comfort and fun, stay at this hotel."

The Aditya Park Hyderabad is a fantastic business hotel which enjoys a great location in the centre of the city and very close to mayor sites of the city. Secundrabad railway station is 7 km away and Shamshababd International Airport is approximately 40 km away. This quality hotel boasts superb rooms and suites of elegant décor and provides a professional service and excellent facilities to guarantee great stay both for business and leisure travellers.

description.content: "Nestled away in the beautiful Baga-Arpora area, this boutique resort overlooks a lovely quaint lagoon that joins Baga beach. The resort is situated 24 kms from Thivim railway station and 33 kms from Karmali railway station. It is approximately 45 kms from Goa airport. The hotel has an outdoor swimming pool and gym. The Balcao is a lively multi-cuisine restaurant open 24 hours a day exclusively for resort guests and is located by the swimming pool. The Ola is an air-conditioned lounge pub and is also located by the swimming pool. The open-air poolside Gazebo is an ideal venue to unwind and laze along the deck facing the lagoon and watch fascinating migratory birds. This luxurious boutique resort is a peaceful and tropical oasis that combines service and exclusive hospitality with the pleasure of a romantic atmosphere. "

The hotel is located in a peaceful and tranquil environment in Betalbatim Goa. It is close (1.8 km) to the longest stretch of virgin white sands on Goa's Colva Beach. The hotel is just 5 km from the city of Margao and 20 minutes from Goa's International Airport Dabolim.

The hotel has got 18 rooms in total, with a mix of local and international design. The large, affordable and spacious rooms offer modern comforts in a rustic local surrounding. Opened in 2007, this air-conditioned hotel has a lobby area with 24-hour reception, bar, restaurant, laundry service (charges apply) and a car park.

The rooms are equipped with ceiling fans, a colour TV with cable connection, international direct dial telephone, mini fridge and tea and coffee making facilities. They all have cosy beds, a well-equipped private bathroom with hot and cold water and shower, a private balcony, Wifi Internet access, electronic key card door locking system and an in-room safe.

There is a swimming pool with children's pool on the hotel's ground.

In the Bamboo Restaurant & Bar guests can relish a variety of delectable delicacies and other savoury concoctions. The hotel offers breakfast, lunch and dinner in a charming ambience. The bar serves cool beverages.

" This hotel enjoys a privileged location within walking distance of the local bus stop, 7 kms from Howrah and Sealdah railway stations and 9 kms from the centre of Kolkata. It lies 25 kms away from Kolkata Airport.Renovated in 2008, this city hotel comprises a total of 122 tastefully designed and equipped rooms and suites. The hotel is equipped with a gym, a health club and a massage room. The Oceanic restaurant is open 24 hours a day and the World Cuisine Restaurant and coffee shop specialise in seafood dishes. Guests can also enjoy the Aaheli, an authentic Bengali restaurant, as well as the Ego bar and a pastry shop. Attention to detail and excellent service will make the guest's stay at this hotel an unforgettable experience."

The luxurious business hotel Grand Sarovar Premiere is conveniently situated in the north of the Mumbai metropolis, on the junction of S.V. Road and Veer Savarkar Flyover. Guests enjoy a range of excellent services and facilities, including a rooftop terrace with outdoor pool and wide open views. The Techniplex Business Center is just 2 minutes away; Oberoi Mall, Film City and the Mindspace Business District can be reached within a short stroll. The Bombay Exhibition Centre is within walking distance. This hotel is an ideal place for business guests.

description.content:
The resort is located in the heart of the Colva, in South Goa and lies less than 100 metres from the beach.

The hotel has a total of 70 rooms spread over 3 floors. Facilities include 24-hour reception, safety deposit lockers, a café, a restaurant, a taxi for rent and currency exchange facilities. There is also a car park for guests arriving by car.

The rooms feature individually regulated air conditioning by means of a ceiling fan, as well as a fridge, double or twin bed, tea/coffee maker, television, telephone and en suite bathroom with WC.

There is an outdoor swimming pool at the hotel which features a children's section. Massage treatments are available for an additional fee. There is also a gym available to guests.

The hotel has a restaurant which serves international cuisine.

Situated in a quiet area near the centre of Calangute, this resort is only 500 metres from the main Calangute Beach and close to other hotels and local amenities such as the Newton supermarket.

This 27-suite hotel was built in classic boutique-style architecture. The accommodation provides fantastic value for money combined with warm and friendly service. The hotel features an air-conditioned lobby with a 24-hour reception, café, bar and restaurant. Internet access is available in public areas and guests are provided with room and laundry services as well. For guests bringing their vehicles, there is a car park in the hotel grounds.

All suites consist of a bedroom, a sitting room and an en suite bathroom. Each suite is tastefully designed and comes with direct dial telephone, 2 televisions, minibar/fridge, tea and coffee making facilities and an in-room safe. All bedrooms are air-conditioned and each suite has a balcony facing the pool.

There is a swimming pool and gym in the hotel grounds.

The multi-cuisine restaurant serves a variety of Goan, Indian, continental and Chinese cuisines.

description.content:
This hotel is located just 5 km from MG Road (Mahatma Gandhi Road) and is conveniently close to the railway station and the bus stop. Guests will find a number of places of interest nearby, including Vidhana Soudha (2 km), the Botanical Gardens (4 km), Bangalore Palace (5 km) and the Iskcon Temple (12 km). The hotel lies only 7 km from Bangalore Airport.

This hotel presents a fabulous alternative to the traditional hotels in Bangalore. It features a sleek and stylish design and offers the perfect combination of comfort and sophistication. This city establishment comprises a total of 44 rooms. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a lobby area with a 24-hour reception, a currency exchange facility, a restaurant and conference facilities. Guests may also take advantage of the room and laundry services and there is parking available for those arriving by car.

The rooms all come with Internet access, air conditioning, a direct dial telephone and cable TV.

There is one restaurant in the hotel which offers a wide choice of dishes.

description.content:
This hotel is located 3 km from the city centre and the railway station is also 3 km away. Near the hotel, guests will find a number of attractions such as Bangalore Palace, which is 2 km away and Cubbon Park, just 3 km away. The hotel lies 36 km from Bangalore Airport.

This city hotel comprises a total of 60 luxurious rooms, including 9 suites. Each room is the epitome of contemporary living, with wide French windows which show a glimpse of the world outside in a truly new light. This cosy hotel is situated far from the madding crowd. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a lobby area with a 24-hour reception, a gift shop, a hairdressing salon, a bar/coffee shop, 2 restaurants and conference facilities. Guests may also take advantage of the laundry service.

The rooms are equipped with a stocked minibar, high-speed Internet access, an electronic safe and a tea/coffee maker. They also come with a direct dial telephone and satellite/cable TV.

The hotel features a health club.

The hotel offers 2 restaurants, 1 serving Thai Chinese food, and another providing a lunchtime buffet. There is also a coffee shop with a variety of menu choices.

This 4 star hotel is located in the city centre of Bangalore. It is a short drive away from the Lal Bagh and the nearest station is n/a. The Hotel has a coffee shop, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness centre/gym. All 99 rooms are equipped with minibar, hairdryer, safe, ironing set and air conditioning.

This resort is located on the virgin Arossim Beach on the south coast of Goa. It lies just 20 minutes from Margao, where guests will find the nearest railway station. The resort is a mere 30 minutes' drive from Dabolim Airport.

The hotel is a beachfront resort, set in the land of golden beaches and swaying palms. This resort offers its guests a never-to-be-forgotten holiday at a heavenly price. This resort comprises a total of 100 rooms and facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility and a cloakroom. Guests are offered a bar, a pub and restaurants, as well as conference facilities and Internet access (charges apply).

 Guests may also take advantage of the laundry service and parking is available for those arriving by car.

The resort offers luxurious accomodation in spacious, well-appointed units which are equipped with all standard international amenities. All rooms come with wonderful garden or pool views. 

The room amenities include a shower, a direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV and tea and coffee making facilities. The rooms also come with an iron and ironing board, a safe, Internet access, a mini fridge and individually adjustable air conditioning. Each room also features either a balcony or a terrace.

description.content:
This hotel is located on the Delhi-Jaipur highway, and the nearest city, Gurgaon, is just 15 minutes from the resort. It lies less than 45 minutes' drive from Delhi International Airport.

This is a Rajasthani-Havelli style palatial resort and invites guests into a world of ethnic grandeur. This boutique hotel comprises a total of 154 rooms including 8 suites, a garden and a terrace and stands for style, eloquence and grandeur. Inspired by the Havellis of Rajasthan and the villages of Punjab and Haryana. The resort echoes the contemporary attitude too and showcases its world class luxury, comfort and hospitality. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a lobby area with a 24-hour reception, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility and a cloakroom. The younger guests can let off steam in the children's playground area with swings. There is a bar, a disco and a restaurant as well as conference facilities and Internet access (charges apply). Guests can also take advantage of the room and laundry services (both for an additional fee) and there is parking available for those arriving by car.

The rooms are designed in an ethnic Rajasthani style, in double-storied clusters or Mohallas. These clusters are interconnected through open archways, imparting a wonderful feeling of freshness and openness. The design rooms combine a contemporary, modern and luxurious look with élan. The design suites, each with either a sit-out terrace or a balcony facing the sprawling main lawns and the swimming pool, offer wonderful views from both the bedroom and the living room. All rooms come with a private bathroom with a shower/bathtub. They are equipped with a direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV, Internet access, a safe, a fridge and a minibar. Furthermore, tea and coffee making facilities and air conditioning units are provided in all accommodation as standard.

"This stunning beach resort is situated amidst lush green surroundings just a 5 minute walk from a spectacular, pristine, sandy beach, making it the ideal choice for visitors who are looking for an escape from the monotony of daily life. Guests will find a selection of shops and restaurants in the vicinity just waiting to be explored. The Portuguese-style hotel was designed with the ultimate in luxury and comfort in mind. Guests will be impressed with the resorts overwhelming sense of calm and serenity allowing it to blend in harmoniously with the natural environment around it. Guests are invited to enjoy sumptuous dining in the resort's hotel where they can sample the delights of a choice of Indian, Goan, Chinese, Mughlai and continental cuisines as well as superb barbeque options, there is something to tempt every palate."

The Marine Plaza is a great boutique hotel strategically situated at the end of Marine Drive, right by Mumbai's business district, a fantastic location from where guests will be able to enjoy great views to the Arabian Sea. The nearest local railway station is Churchgate, which is within walking distance and the Victoria Terminus station is about 8-10 minutes away. This luxury hotel provides guests with unparalleled service, fabulous views and exquisite décor showcasing a perfect blend of the East and the West.

This 3 star hotel is located in the city centre of Kochi. It is close to the Bolgatty Island. The Hotel has a coffee shop, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness centre/gym. All 50 rooms are equipped with minibar and air conditioning.

Centrally situated in Karol Bagh, Delhi's prime shopping and business hub, the hotel TJS Royale is strategically positioned in the Indian capital. Its location provides easy access to all major attractions of the city; Karol Bagh metro station is just 300 m away. Connaught Place and the government area are within easy reach, and New Delhi Train Station can be reached within a short drive. The domestic airport and Indira Gandhi International Airport are at a distance of 13 km and 16 km, respectively.
The hotel offers elegant and well-appointed rooms with air-conditioning and complimentary WIFI internet connection. This hotel features stylish and contemporary design, a lavish reception and a lobby, large 3-storey atrium and a 9-metre waterfall running through all floors. The property has 33 tastefully designed rooms, equipped to meet today's corporate requirements. The two conference halls ensure that business meetings can be conducted effortlessly. Further facilities at the air-conditioned hotel include a restaurant, conference facilities, and both room and laundry services.
The hotel provides tastefully designed rooms, equipped with all modern amenities like a minibar, tea/coffee maker, large flat-screen TV, Internet access and an electronic safe. Each room is designed to offer rest and relaxation in a way that is subtle and unobtrusive. The rooms are also en suite featuring a shower and a bath.
There is a multi-cuisine restaurant at the hotel that serves Indian and continental dishes.

Located in the heart of South Delhi at Nehru Place, Asia's largest IT hub, minutes away from the metro and market, The Muse Sarovar Portico is also closely connected to Noida, Gurgaon and the business hubs of Okhla, Jasola, Chanakyapuri and Faridabad. This gives you the advantage of quick access without any traffic challenges. The hotel is just 15 kms from the international airport and 13 kms from the railway station.  Contemporary amenities and professional service deliver value par excellence especially for business travellers. Leisure travellers won't be disappointed either and will find upscale shopping centres like Greater Kailash and South Extension a short drive away. The Lotus Temple, Iskcon Temple, Akshardham Temple and Saket City Walk Mall are nearby. Elegantly designed and exquisitely furnished 42 guest rooms, multi-cuisine dining and a state of art business centre make this the perfect choice for travellers seeking modern comforts at affordable prices.

Business or pleasure, whatever the purpose of your trip to New Delhi, the location of your Hotel should be convenient, comfortable and affordable. Regale Inn offers you just that: outstanding location and comfort - all at an affordable price.The hotel provides excellent facilities for holding conferences and events in New Delhi.For any traveller who appreciates the value of cleanliness and space, this hotel stands just for that. The hotel premises, rooms and facilities are spic and span. The hotel is ideal for travellers on the move.Hotel Regale Inn is located in the most popular region of India's capital city, Chittranjan Park in South Delhi. It is very convenient for guests visiting Delhi for leisure or visiting companies in and around Nehru Place.

description.content: Designer Business Hotel centrally & conveniently located in the upmarket locality of South Delhi & in close proximity (3 kms) to business centres like Connaught Place, 25 minutes from domestic Airport & within walking distance from the famous Exhibition grounds “Pragati Maidan” where all national & international exhibitions are held. It is located in the most exclusive commercial and residential area of New Delhi. It is a 30 minutes drive from the International Airport & 15 min. drive from the New Delhi Railway Station.Offering bed & breakfast rates, “Shervani New Delhi” is replete with contemporary in-room facilities, modern amenities & peaceful Environment. Hotel consists of centrally air-conditioned Standard, Deluxe, Premium & Suite rooms all elegantly furnished. All the rooms have attached bathrooms with 24 hours hot & cold running water, Electronic door lock, LED Flat Screen TV with satellite connection, Mood Lighting, Direct dial Telephone, Minibar, Electronic Safe & Internet Wi-Fi Connection. Equipped with a ‘Cafe' that serves both Indian & Continental dishes, it makes a perfect venue for business travelers & tourists.

This 4 star hotel is located close to the airport of New Delhi and was established in 1993. It is a short drive away from the Shiv Murti. The Hotel has a coffee shop, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness centre/gym. All 82 rooms are equipped with minibar, hairdryer, ironing set and air conditioning.

The hotel is located 15 km from Connaught Place in Delhi's city centre. There are shopping opportunities nearby, as is the commercial centre of Gurgaon. The international/domestic airport is approximately 4 km from the hotel.

This hotel has established itself as the ideal choice for both business and leisure travellers. The hotel, with its lush green lawn and surroundings, offers the perfect blend of contemporary amenities and traditional hospitality. With aesthetically designed rooms, it promises to offer an inimitable experience and make guests feel the personal and warm hospitality. Facilities at the air-conditioned hotel include a lobby, bar, restaurant, conference facilities, and both room and laundry services.

The hotel provides centrally air-conditioned and aesthetically designed rooms equipped with facilities such as Internet access, a minibar, TV, telephone and work desk. Each also features an en suite bathroom with a shower and bath.

Guests may take a plunge in the outdoor swimming pool or stroll around the landscaped gardens.

Guests can visit the 24-hour coffee shop for an excellent selection of food items and delicious flavoured coffee the way they like it. The multi-cuisine restaurant is synonymous with an exotic dining experience owing to the outstanding cuisine, crisp environment and exemplary service. A transcending milieu and an aura embodying the celebratory vision of life and friendship contribute to the refined ambiance.

The hotel is located in Delhi's modern and electric satellite city Gurgaon. The embassy district is about 20 minutes away while the domestic and international airports are also nearby.

The hotel is centrally air-conditioned and has been constructed to create an ambience of luxury and style. All the rooms are equipped with modern amenities to make the each guest's stay comfortable and enjoyable. Guests are welcomed in a lobby, while facilities include a restaurant, conference facilities, and both room and laundry services.

The hotel provides comfortable rooms with personal services and modern amenities such as a TV, telephone, safety deposit box, minibar and a tea/coffee maker. The en suite bathrooms have a bathtub and a shower.

The bar and restaurant serves Indian, Chinese, continental and Mughlai dishes. National and international liquor brands and a variety of cocktails are available for guests. Experienced chefs provide a variety of barbecue snacks to accompany a cocktail. The coffee shop with elegant décor caters for the varied tastes of different guests.

The hotel is located on Janpath Road, New Delhi, just 20 km from the airport.

The hotel offers its guests a home away from home and a comfortable stay. Guests at the beautifully designed hotel experience world-class hospitality with a personal touch. Guests are welcomed in a lobby with 24-hour check-out service. Further facilities include air conditioning, a restaurant, conference facilities and a laundry service.

The hotel provides centrally air-conditioned rooms with a private bathroom with a shower and bath. Further in-room amenities include a direct dial telephone, Internet access, a minibar, satellite/cable TV and a safety deposit box.

The 24-hour coffee shop serves a breakfast buffet, lunch and dinner, while an à la carte menu and health food delicacies like eggs and sugar-free desserts are also available. The hotel also features a specialty restaurant.

This business-class hotel is located 1 km from the city centre of Delhi. Being located in the centre of the Business Hub – Inner Circle Connaught Place the hotel is the prime choice of tourists and business delegates from around the world. The property contains 87 air-conditioned rooms. Each room is elegantly furnished and equipped with direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV and radio. The hotel offers doctor on call, currency exchange facilities, souvenir shop, a hairdressing salon, and much more. Conference facilities, room service, a laundry service and a car park are also available. The hotel restaurant offers predominantly Indian cuisine.

The hotel is located in Chanakyapuri, 6 km from Connaught Place, 9 km from New Delhi Railway Station, 10 km from the domestic airport and 15 km from the international airport.

Set in beautifully landscaped gardens, this elegant stone and marble structure is set around a central flower-filled atrium and open-air courtyard. The rooms and deluxe apartments overlook the enclosed gardens, fountains and water channels, while also satisfying the demands of the most discerning guests. Facilities at the air-conditioned hotel include a lobby, 3 restaurants, conference facilities, and both room and laundry services.

The hotel provides rooms equipped with amenities including a telephone, satellite/cable TV, piped music, a minibar, Internet access, hairdryer and safety deposit box. The rooms are also en suite with a shower and bath. Each room is designed to offer rest and relaxation to accommodate the needs of both business and leisure travellers.

To fulfil the entertainment needs of guests, the hotel features facilities like a swimming pool, health club, beauty parlour and tennis court.

There are three restaurants at the hotel. One serves Indian and Mughlai cuisine with Indian Ghazals (live), the other serves Chinese cuisine while a multi-cuisine restaurant, as well as a pub and bar also feature.

Welcome to The Ashok! Set upon 25 acres of prime land in the Capital's diplomatic area, the hotel's world class services and amenities pamper presidents, celebrities, and distinguished clientele with traditional Indian hospitality. Ever responsive to the needs of the time it offers convention tourism for national and international conferences, luxury rooms and suites, an array of international cuisine experiences, supplemented with a health club and destination health spa and a business center.The Ashok's hospitality, high level comfort, quality services and catering to its distinguished clientele has made it a name to reckon with in the country.

This hotel is situated in the central business district of Pune. It is near to the Software Technology Park and just 300 m from the Deccan Gymkhana bus stop. Pune railway station is 4 km away and it is just 12 km to the airport.

The hotel caters perfectly to guests' needs and attends to their requirements in surroundings of luxurious opulence. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a lobby area with a 24-hour reception and check-out service, a hotel safe, a currency exchange facility, a hairdressing salon and a games room. There is a cafe and a restaurant and guests can take advantage of the room and laundry services.

The well appointed guest rooms, featuring soft furnishings, all come with a private bathroom with a shower/bathtub and a hairdryer. They are equipped with a direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV, Internet access and a fridge. Furthermore, air conditioning and tea and coffee making facilities are provided in all accommodation as standard and the rooms provide all modern amenities.

The hotel is located on Viman Nagar in Pune, very close to the IT Park and just 8 km from Pune airport.

An exemplary blend of excellent service and state-of-the-art facilities, this hotel is one of the most happening places for conference, seminars, banquets, parties and meetings, fulfilling the needs of business travellers and providing the best comfort and luxury for those looking for truly relaxing leisure time. The air-conditioned hotel offers 61 rooms and a lobby, restaurant, conference facilities, and room and laundry services.

All of the centrally air-conditioned rooms in the hotel are well furnished with unmatched comfort and feature a range of room facilities, such as an en suite bathroom with a shower, bathtub and hot and cold running water, a minibar, satellite TV and Internet access.

The multi-cuisine restaurant in the hotel serves Indian, Chinese and continental dishes.

This airport hotel enjoys a convenient location in the hub of the business district on Dhole Patil Road. Its close proximity to Pune Airport and to the railway station (24 km), as well as to tourist attractions and recreational facilities, makes this compact hotel an ideal choice for both business and leisure travellers.

This hotel offers a unique blend of impeccable service, sophistication and warm hospitality. It has been serving travellers from across the globe for well over two decades and has a cheery staff on hand to give guests a warm welcome upon their arrival. After long hours of travel, the lobby is an inviting place for a refreshing drink, and features a 24-hour reception and currency exchange facilities. Guests will also find a café and room and laundry services on site.

The rooms have been tastefully decorated in cheerful tones. Guests may relax on the comfortable beds and enjoy a favourite show on the cable TV, or order an in-room movie. The desks come with broadband Internet access and allow guests to work efficiently and effectively. All guest rooms have a host of amenities that include room service, electronic safes, direct dial telephones, minibars, tea and coffee making facilities, and showers.

The hotel has an in-house health club.

The multi-cuisine restaurant offers an array of food to satisfy guests' taste buds that features a diverse range of Indian and continental cuisine, as well as a sumptuous buffet breakfast. The weary traveller can always order room service in the comfort of their hotel room.

"This luxurious hotel is located approximately 1 kms from the city centre and 3 kms from the Pune railway station. Ideal for business and pleasure trips, it features central air-conditioning, currency exchange facilities and a laundry service.Apart from the leisurely outdoor pool, guests can take advantage of a complete gym with hot tub, steam room, sauna facilities, massage treatments, modern equipment and professional instructors. Guests can enjoy a diverse menu featuring continental and Chinese cuisine at the Casablanca fine dining restaurant and coffee shop. The Puran Da Dhaba restaurant features rustic ambience and serves an extensive buffet daily with live Indian music. Guests may also relax in contemporary luxury of the X'tasy Grill Room and bar. "

"This budget hotel is located in close proximity to several of the city's commercial and shopping areas. Wiekfield IT Park - one of the city's major business centres. Equally suitable for business and leisurely travels, it is only 3 kms away from the airport.Fondly called as the Oxford of the East and the cultural capital of Maharashtra, Pune as a city has grown rapidly over the past few decades. Pune has the highest number of software companies in India-212, followed by Bengaluru - 208, Hyderabad – 97, hence called the Silicon Valley of Maharashtra. The hotel offers a health club, 24-hour coffee shop and a restaurant serving a blend of international and local cuisines, where guests can order a full daily board as well as separate breakfast, lunch and dinner options. "

The hotel is located on the Bombay-Pune motorway.

The air-conditioned hotel offers rooms with luxury amenities to ensure a comfortable stay. Facilities include a lobby with 24-hour reception, lift access, around-the-clock room service and a car park.

The guest rooms are tastefully and elegantly furnished and well equipped with every possible comfort, such as satellite TV, a direct dial telephone, Internet access, individually regulated air conditioning and an en suite bathroom to name but a few. These facilities add comfort and luxury to any guest's stay at the hotel.

After a hectic schedule of business conferences and seminars, guests can make use of the health club to unwind and relax.

Dining options at the hotel include an in-house restaurant which serves delectable dishes taken from the menu featuring Chinese, continental and Indian cuisines. The restaurant has its very own in-house chef who is an expert in catering to the various tastes of guests. The mouth-watering dishes served in the restaurant are sure to leave guests asking for more. The hotel also has a well-stocked bar which serves a good assortment of drinks.

This luxurious hotel features a strategic location just a short driving distance from the airport, offering the perfect base from which to explore all the hidden treasures of Pune, the seventh largest metropolis in India considered the cultural capital of Maharashtra. This award-winning property enjoys a convenient situation close to some of the most important tourist attractions in the region including Pataleshwar Caves, situated just a 20-minute drive away, Aga Khan Palace, and Raja Dinkar Kelkar Museum. Ideal for business and leisure travellers alike, this luxurious property offers a wide choice of outstanding accommodation units to suit all clients' needs. Those most demanding customers may prefer the stunning club room, featuring VIP amenities such as turn down service. The cosy restaurant is one of India's first teppanyaki sytle restaurants. It serves some of the most exotic delicacies of the region.

This hotel is located at Pune's most upcoming location, Kalyani Nagar, just 7 km away from the airport.

This hotel is for global business corporate guests. The hotel offers 71 suites fully equipped to cater to the needs of corporate travellers and it also offers comforts and facilities which meet international standards. This hotel has large room sizes with beautiful interiors to make one feel at home. Guests are welcomed into a lobby with a hotel safe and currency exchange facilities at this air-conditioned establishment. There is a restaurant on-site and conference facilities available to business travellers. Guests can also take advantage of the hotel's room and laundry services and those arriving by car may park their vehicle in the hotel's car park.

The hotel has elegant and modern style spacious suites with all modern comforts and facilities. Each one has an en suite bathroom with a shower and bath. Amenities such as a tea/coffee maker, an in-room kitchenette with an induction plate, an iron with ironing board, a hairdryer, a well-stocked minibar and electronic safe lockers are standard in all suites. Furthermore, a direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV and Internet access make keeping in touch easy.

To rejuvenate their energy, guests can make use of the health club in the hotel which features a gym.

There is a multi-cuisine restaurant, a lounge bar and a coffee shop in the hotel.

description.content:
The city hotel is situated on Sadhu Vaswani Circle, just a 5-minute walk from Pune railway station.

The air-conditioned hotel offers 100 rooms catering to executive travellers. Facilities include a lobby with a hotel safe, currency exchange facilities, a cafe and restaurant, room and laundry services, and a car park.

The hotel offers clean and simple accommodation options to its guests, with deluxe, air-conditioned and non-air-conditioned rooms. The rooms are all set in quiet and peaceful surroundings and in-room amenities include a direct dial telephone, satellite TV, Internet access and tea and coffee making facilities.

The restaurant within the hotel offers a fine range of authentic Indian, Chinese and continental cuisine.

This apartment hotel is located at Sanewai, Aundh. It lies just 16 km from Pune Airport.

The hotel offers its guests modern amenities with all the comforts. The establishment aims to replicate the cosiness of home and to offer a high standard of service. Facilities available at the hotel include dining options such as a restaurant and a bar.

Guests staying in these apartments will enjoy a high level of spatial comfort and hospitality.

There is an outdoor, rooftop, temperature-controlled swimming pool for guests' use. Other leisure facilities include a hot tub, a steam room and a massage chair. Those looking to stay in shape can visit the on-site gym for a work-out.

The lounge bar serves a variety of cocktails and snacks, with nightly entertainment and a live DJ to set the mood. The hotel also features a fine dining restaurant that offers a unique interpretation of world cuisine with recipes drawn from many cultures, using local and organic ingredients. There is also a rooftop bar and fusion grill restaurant, which is open for dinner in a candle-lit atmosphere, marked by outstanding fusion food and exotic music.

Located on M.G. Road, the hotel is in the heart of the city of Pune, and just 1 km away from the railway station and bus terminal and 9 km from the airport.

The hotel's proximity to some of the leading business houses in the city makes it extremely convenient to the discerning business traveller who is generally hard-pressed for time. The establishment is air-conditioned and welcomes guests in a lobby. There is a restaurant on-site and conference facilities available to business travellers. Guests can also take advantage of the hotel's room and laundry services.

The hotel offers exquisitely appointed and furnished rooms which are elegantly designed to meet the taste of modern travellers. Each room has an en suite bathroom with shower/bath. Rooms come with all facilities on-hand such as cable TV with 24-hour satellite channels, Internet access, a well stocked minibar, a tea/coffee maker, a hairdryer on request and a safety deposit locker.

A superior health club with a gym and an outdoor swimming pool serve for those wanting recreational entertainment.

There are two restaurants serving Thai, Chinese, Japanese, Indian and Continental cuisines. The 24-hour coffee shop is the most happening place in the city open throughout the night. The lounge bar located at lobby level always enthrals guests when the in-house DJ is present and it is a rocking place for those who enjoy a drink, as it serves all leading brands as well as delightful mocktails.

Soaring high above the up-market Koregaon Park area, which is famous for its business establishments and multi-cuisine restaurants, this hotel enjoys a strategic location in Rajiv Gandhi Infotech Park, Hinjewadi. It lies only 2 km from the railway station, 7 km from Pune Airport and 190 km from Mumbai International Airport.

This is a smart and sophisticated business hotel in Pune, and offers the ideal environment for discerning corporate guests. Facilities on offer to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a lobby area with a 24-hour reception and check-out service and a restaurant. Business travellers will appreciate the conference facilities and guests can also take advantage of the room and laundry services. There is parking available for those arriving by car.

All rooms come with a private bathroom with a shower/bathtub and a hairdryer. They are equipped with a direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV, Internet access, a safe, a minibar and a fridge. Furthermore, tea and coffee making facilities, an ironing set and air conditioning are provided in all accommodation as standard.

The hotel features a beauty salon and guests can take a refreshing dip in the outdoor swimming pool or work out and rejuvenate at the gym. It is also possible to sweat it out in the steam room or relax with a spa treatment.

The hotel's multi-cuisine restaurant serves all kinds of mouth-watering dishes.

The hotel is 7 km away from Pune Airport; 2 km away from the Railway Station and 190 km away from the Mumabi International Airport.

"This elegant resort is conveniently located on Varca beach, one of the most magnificent beaches in Goa. It is near the major tourist attractions and shopping hubs. The beach resort is spread on a sprawling 14-acre property with a lush tropical paradise that promises the guests a picture-perfect vacation. During high tourist season, the hotel organises theme evening complete with a live band, karaoke nights, magic shows and more which makes it an ideal place for leisure as well as for business conferences or team building activities. Leisure facilities available at this establishment include a swimming pool, with a separate pool for toddlers, live evening entertainment, indoor board games and table tennis. The resort's multi-cuisine restaurant serves variety of options."

"This boutique-style beach resort in Goa is located on the sunset side of the Calangute - Candolim beach belt of North Goa, just a 500-metre stroll from the beach.
It offers features charming architecture inspired by its Portuguese heritage. Guests can breathe in the air of the sea and dine to the sound of the waves breaking on the shore. The rooms of the resort are tastefully decorated, comfortable and spacious, equipped with all modern amenities. The resort provides outdoor swimming pool, indoor and outdoor games, a gym as well as beauty salon and an Ayurvedic massage centre to help guests to relax, rejuvenate and pamper themselves. There is also a multi-cuisine restaurant that offers plenty of flavours and bars, which provides chilled drinks to keep ones senses tingling."

With the idyllic setting of Calangute as its backdrop, Adamo The Bellus re-creates the magic of Goa in a beautiful setting with 150 luxurious rooms to suit your Goan holiday moods! It's a place where every day is a celebration and you are the occasion!

The Bellus offers a soothing blend of warm, effortless service and harmonious spaces, while preserving traditional Goan décor and spirit. Each room is furnished in natural tones and textures and offers spectacular views. The interiors highlight the fine craftsmanship and attention to detail that distinguishes us from the rest and seamlessly extends the magic of Goa's blessed natural beauty in its design, while offering the finest in contemporary luxuries and services.

The Bellus also offers a wide range of activities to relax and rejuvenate – whether it is a signature wellness experience at the La Soin Spa, a leisurely Goan tour past ancient churches and monuments or a game of ping-pong at our indoor games centre.
Experience the pleasure of being pampered as you relax, unwind and rejuvenate at the Bellus.
 
This beautiful resort is situated just 400 meters from Calangute Beach. It is 12 km from Panji, 22 km from the Thivim railway station, and 45 km from the airport. This cosy resort, surrounded by palm trees, is located a few minutes away from the golden sands of the world acclaimed ‘Queen of Beaches', Calangute Beach.

The hotel offers well-equipped, beautifully decorated rooms with individual balconies. The hospitable and well-mannered employees provide the highest standard of service. Guests can lay back and relax by the swimming pool, where the restaurant serves an array of delicious culinary delights. The guests also have access to other facilities such as a gym, a hot tub, a sauna, a steam bath and a massage centre.

This resort offers a convenient location by Utorda Beach in South Goa. It is just 15 minutes from Margao railway station and is some 20 minutes from Dabolim Airport. Nestled in the white sands of Utorda Beach, it sprawls across 14 acres. 

On-site dining options include a number of restaurants, a café, a lounge bar and a disco. There is also a casino at the hotel.  The rooms are a reflection of the bygone Portuguese era. The traditional décor is enhanced with modern day luxuries to make guests' stays as comfortable as possible. For the final touch, guests can step out onto a private balcony to take in the splendid view of the Arabian Sea and the softly lapping waters of the landscaped pool. 

The hotel services in the Health and Beauty category make the resort a lifestyle statement with its rejuvenating massages at the spa and the pampering beauty treatments at the beauty parlour.

The resort is situated on a 26 km. stretch of soft white sand in South Goa. It is located 15 min from Dabolim International Airport and 10 min from Margao Konkan Railway Station.


The resort features 120 spacious rooms spread over 22 acres of lush green landscape, with luxurious ambience. Each of these rooms offers a private balcony, with spectacular views of either the ocean or the tropical gardens.

A number of facilities are offered by the resort such as separate health and fitness centres for ladies and gents, indoor and outdoor pools, squash court, tennis court, billiards, carom table, massage therapy, chess and other board games and beach volley ball. There is also a refreshing hydrotherapeutic whirlpool, steam and sauna, a fully equipped gymnasium, plus a variety of gaming facilities including tennis, squash and billiards. Spin the roulette wheel at Goa's latest casino is also available.

The Tea Lounge and Bar serves tropical drinks and light snacks has a sophisticated atmosphere for cocktails and conversation. For a unique dining experience, guests may try the multi-cuisine restaurant. The Coffee Shop is overlooking Goa's only indoor pool and offers a friendly welcome.

The hotel is located at Lindsay street, just 20 km away from the airport.

The hotel provides rooms with all modern facilities like Direct Dial Telephones, Mini Bar, Colour Cable T/V and Tea / coffee maker.

On the 9th floor of the hotel, there is a multi cuisine restaurant uniquely designed in three different themes. The ambiance of a high - class restaurant, "Terrace" with natural surroundings and the vibrant "High Spirits" bar with a breath taking view of Kolkata is sure to exceed expectations. Coupled with the gastronomic delights of the chefs here, it is sure that the experience will become a habit. Serving Indian, Chinese and Continental dishes, the menu is carefully designed to suit one's palate.

description.content: The stylish design hotel The Park Kolkata is a fascinating boutique style experience and excellently situated on the Park Street, the shopping and entertainment centre of Kolkata. This luxurious hotel offers guests first-class services and amenities, such as the 24-hour restaurant The Bridge featuring a 17 metre waterfall. Attractions such as the Indian National Museum, Birla Planetarium, the Victoria Memorial or Eden Gardens are within a short stroll from the hotel. This is a great choice for guests who wish to explore one of India's most famous cities.

Park Palace Hotel is a government-approved hotel that is situated at Gariahat Road, Kolkata. A budget hotel in a prime location, 20 KM away from Dum Dum airport and 10 KM from Howrah Railway Station and at a walking distance from Gariahat Bus Stand, the hotel is quite popular among corporates and tourists.The Hotel serves customers with more than 29 fully air-conditioned double bed rooms. Charges for these rooms start from Rs. 2500 onwards, excluding tax. Amenities and services provided at the hotel include 24-hour room service, telephone, currency exchange, car rental, dry cleaning and valet parking. You can relish from a wide variety of cuisines served which includes Chinese, continental, and South and North Indian menus.

Located in the very heart of the city, the hotel is only minutes away from both the business hub and the major shopping malls and markets. The local railway station is around 25 minutes away by car. Nicco Park is around an hour's drive. Tourist attractions are nearby such as Fountain of Joy and Indian Museum around 1.5 km away, Shahid Minar approximately 2.5 km away and Birla Temple roughly 3 km away. Netaji Subhash Chandra Bose International Airport is located approximately 15 km from the hotel.

Established in 1947, the hotel then had 42 rooms and two bungalows, but has now grown to a 105-room deluxe hotel under the present management which has nurtured it since 1967. As a hotel with a history, it lives up to its colonial benchmarks of service and takes pride in its warm and friendly employees and impeccable customer care. This air-conditioned city hotel offers a lobby, bar, restaurant, conference facilities, room service and laundry service.

The hotel rooms are furnished with not only the most tasteful and enlivening decor, but also the most comfortable and practical amenities to ensure a relaxing and satisfying stay. The facilities include individually regulated air conditioning, and an in-room digital safe and direct dial telephone. Further amenities include an en suite bathroom, satellite/cable TV, Internet access, minibar and tea and coffee making facilities.

Guests can stay fit in the well-equipped health club with its multi gym facilities, enjoy the Ayurvedic, herbal and aromatic therapeutic massages or relax in the sauna and steam bath.

In the hotel, guests will discover a culture through cuisine. From the English pub with its glorious past to the multi cuisine at the hotel restaurants, a mesmerising dining experience is ensured.

This hotel is located by Juhu - Mumbai's happening beach and the heart of the city. The establishment lies some 7 km from the domestic and international airports.

This hotel is a place where the age-old values of hospitality and courtesy blend smoothly with the new-age virtues of service, efficiency and quality. The establishment offers a home away from home for both intrepid tourists and jet-weary business travellers and features an on-site bar-restaurant.

Neat and comfortable, these guest rooms are tastefully decorated. They offer a simple elegance and give guests a delightful welcome when they return after a hectic day outdoors.

The hotel's swimming pool has crystal-clear waters that are so blue that guests could easily spend all day there. Meanwhile, Body-One is a revolutionised, centrally air-conditioned gym, which provides scientific and professional guidance towards a healthier society.

The hotel bar cum restaurant serves a range of cuisine and cocktails.

The corporate Mumbai Bombay Stock Exchange, Colaba, Nariman Point, Worli and Lower Parel are just 15 minutes away. The railway station is around 5 km from the hotel and the bus station around 2 km. It is 23 km away from the Chhatrapati Shivaji International Airport.

This city hotel offers excellent service for holiday travellers, and features meeting and conference facilities for business travellers to make their workshops and conferences more comfortable and convenient. The air-conditioned hotel has a lobby with safe, currency exchange facilities, lift access, café, bar and restaurant. Room service, laundry service and a car park are also available.

The 96 tastefully furnished rooms are designed to anticipate the needs of business travellers. The interior is designed with colours and textures to soothe tired eyes. They are equipped with hairdryer, direct dial telephone, satellite/cable TV, fridge, tea and coffee making facilities, a balcony or terrace and safe.

The hotel's restaurant has well-laid-out, generous buffets with a choice of Indian, continental and Chinese fare for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Guests can enjoy a quick and full meal without fuss or delay.

The hotel is centrally located at Vileparle, very close to the domestic airport which is 1 km away and the international airport which is 3 km away.

The unique location of this hotel makes it an ideal choice for the traveller, offering the best of both worlds - business as well as pleasure, with the utmost in comfort and unsurpassed hospitality. It is luxuriously appointed with amenities that ensure a comfortable and productive stay. This air-conditioned establishment welcomes its guests in a lobby with a hotel safe and currency exchange facilities. There is a restaurant and a bar on-site and conference facilities are on-hand for business travellers. Guests can take advantage of the hotel's room and laundry services. Those arriving by car may park their vehicles in the hotel's car park.
